Interface CommandOnWidgets

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Command, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ONOFFCommand, RefreshViewCommand, VisibilityCommand

    public interface CommandOnWidgets
extends Command
    A representation of the model object 'Command On Widgets'. Classe astratta da cui discendono i comandi che agiscono su un elenco di widget, o di elementi di menu

    The following features are supported:

    • Target Widgets
    • Target Menu Element
